<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_94" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_94_r2l1">Burggraf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l2"><expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu hohenloch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l3">Bẏſſchoff cʒu <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l4"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> Grafen cʒu VVertheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l5"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Pıckenbach vnd <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>graf</expan> cʒu <expan>Mıltenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l6">hanman Achtern vıcʒtume cʒu <expan>Aſſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l7">Bẏſſchoff cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_94_r2l8">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir Bıtten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute / vnd auch Jr hab vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l10">in die nehſtkünftigen herbſtmeſſe gen frankfurt / vnd vvider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l11">darauſʒ mit geleẏte <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle / Alſo vvenn ſie 
<add><ab facs="#facs_94_line_1574683595721_791">oder die Jren </ab></add> darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l12">cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden / oder aber ~ den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des begern / daʒ ſıe <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l13">durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> lande / herſchaft vnd gepiete ſıcher beleẏtet werden / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l14">Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd bıten des ewr gnedıg <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l15">vvıder cʒu vviſſen beẏ <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iij̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Laurentij </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l17">Anno M<hi rend="sup">o</hi> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi> vııȷ<hi rend="sup">uo</hi> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_94" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burggraf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, <lb/><expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Hohenloch, <lb/>bysschoff czu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, grafen czu Wertheim,
                            <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                        Pickenbach und <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>graf</expan> czu
                            <expan>Miltenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <lb/>Hanman Achtern, vicztume czu
                                <expan>Asschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <lb/>bysschoff czu Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir bitten
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute und auch ir hab und
                        kauffmanschaft in die nehstkünftigen herbstmesse gen Frankfurt und wider
                        darausz mit geleyte <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle. Also wenn sie <add>oder die
                            iren</add> darümb czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden oder aber den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und des begern, daz sie
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> lande,
                        herschaft und gepiete sicher beleytet werden, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und biten des ewr gnedig
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider czu wissen bey
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Laurentii
                        anno m<hi rend="sup">o</hi> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi> viii<hi rend="sup">vo</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
